        "sheet": {
          "explanation": {
            "intent": "Experimental lo-fi electronica with Dilla-feel drums, sparse Voder syllables floating in and out, Buchla plucks adding textural grain, Rhodes carrying a slow melancholic melody, and warm sub-bass anchoring a minor key progression",
            "style": "LO-FI / EXPERIMENTAL ELECTRONICA",
            "section": "verse1",
            "energy": 0.38,
            "key": "D minor",
            "progression": "Dm - Bb - F - C (2 bars each)",
            "rhythm": "Dilla displaced kick/snare, irregular closed hats with wide velocity swings, sparse open hats, ghost snares on unexpected 16ths",
            "orchestration": "Drums MS-20 anchor, Pro-One sub-bass with walking roots, Rhodes EP slow melodic phrases, HybridSynth Pads long sustain chords, Buchla sparse plucks, Voder sporadic phoneme bursts"
