            "intent": "Hopeful lo-fi electronica instrumental — key lifts to D major, full groove locks in with Dilla-feel drums, Buchla plucks now melodic and bright, Rhodes carries an optimistic ascending phrase, warm pads swell with major chord voicings, Voder hums vowel-bright syllables, bass walks with purpose",
