          "explanation": {
            "intent": "Bridge — tension peak with partial breakdown: bass stripped to root-only long notes, pads thinned to single sustained dissonant chord with slow CC swell, Buchla drops out entirely, Rhodes plays sparse stabbed chords on unexpected beats, drums strip to kick+snare skeleton with open hats and sudden silences, Voder carries long exposed phoneme wails (ER/AH/UW) with high brightness and vibrato for emotional intensity",
            "style": "LO-FI / EXPERIMENTAL ELECTRONICA",
            "section": "bridge",
            "energy": 0.68,
            "key": "D major",
            "progression": "Bm - G - D - A (2 bars each, darker modal feel)",
            "rhythm": "Stripped skeleton — kick on 1 only, snare displaced and sparse, open hat stabs, long silences, sudden accent hits, no constant hi-hat pulse",
            "orchestration": "Drums bare and exposed with silences, bass roots only held long, pads single thin dissonant chord with slow filter swell, no Buchla, Rhodes rare stabs, Voder long wailing phrases with high vibrato and brightness"
