        "sheet": {
          "explanation": {
            "intent": "Verse3 — full return with maximum energy: all layers back in full force, drums dense and driving with ghost notes and syncopated hats, bass walking active lines with filter movement, pads layered with full chord voicings and rhythmic stabs, Buchla re-enters with aggressive textural sweeps, Rhodes comping busily on offbeats, Voder delivering punchy short phoneme bursts with brighter timbre and less vibrato than bridge — everything pushing forward with urgency and momentum",
            "style": "LO-FI / EXPERIMENTAL ELECTRONICA",
            "section": "verse3",
            "energy": 0.74,
            "key": "D major",
            "progression": "Bm - G - D - A (2 bars each)",
            "rhythm": "Full groove — kick on 1 and syncopated 16ths, snare on 2&4 with ghosts and displacement, constant varied hi-hat pulse with open hat stabs, clap reinforcement, tom fills entering at phrase ends",
            "orchestration": "Full drum kit with ghost notes and syncopation, bass active walking lines with CC filter sweeps, pads full chord stabs with rhythmic push, Buchla re-enters with textural noise bursts, Rhodes busy offbeat comping, Voder short punchy phrases with bright phonemes"
