      {
        "sheet": {
          "explanation": {
            "intent": "Outro — gradual dissolution and resolution: elements drop out one by one across 8 bars, drums thin to sparse kick and occasional hat by bar 5, bass simplifies to long held roots with slow filter close, pads sustain long open voicings fading in velocity, Buchla removed, Rhodes drops after bar 4, Voder delivers one final slow exhale phrase in bars 1-2 then fades, leaving only a whisper of kick and pad shimmer by the end",
            "style": "LO-FI / EXPERIMENTAL ELECTRONICA",
            "section": "outro",
            "energy": 0.42,
            "key": "D major",
            "progression": "Bm - G - D - A (2 bars each, slowing in density)",
            "rhythm": "Sparse kick pattern, minimal hats dropping out over time, no clap, no ghost notes after bar 3, snare disappears by bar 5, only occasional kick remains by bar 7",
            "orchestration": "Drums thinning across 8 bars, bass long root notes with filter closing, pads slow sustained chords decreasing in velocity, Rhodes drops after bar 4, Voder one final slow phrase, Buchla absent throughout"
          },
          "bpm": 82,
          "tension": 0.38,
