        "sheet": {
          "explanation": {
            "intent": "Instrumental — full groove lock-in across 8 bars, no vocals, all instruments driving hard: kick/snare backbone with displaced hits and ghost notes, rolling closed hats with varied velocity, bass pumping with syncopated fills, pads layered and bright, Rhodes comping rhythmically, Buchla adding textural sweeps, Voder wordless vowel-drone for color. Progression cycles Bm-G-D-A twice then Bm-G-Em-A twice. Tension and energy elevated into full-band groove territory.",
            "style": "LO-FI / EXPERIMENTAL ELECTRONICA",
            "section": "instrumental",
            "energy": 0.58,
            "key": "D major",
            "progression": "Bm - G - D - A (2 bars each, cycling twice over 8 bars)",
            "rhythm": "Four-on-the-floor kick with displaced snare hits, ghost notes on snare, busy closed hat with velocity variation, occasional open hat on offbeats, clap on bar 3 of each 4-bar phrase, toms sprinkled for fills",
            "orchestration": "Full drums, syncopated bass with filter sweeps, pads wide voicings at medium velocity, Rhodes rhythmic stabs, Buchla textural swells, Voder wordless vowel drone mid-section"
